quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, miim."
  26,2,"∆äeen ko aayeeje Deftere …ďanngunde nde."
  26,3,"Mbelejo'o an a tampiniray hoore maa…óa kin fii …ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,4,"Si Min muuyii Min njippinat e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka kammu aaya daa…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen √Īalla ko …óe yankinanii…óe mo."
  26,5,"Arataa e ma…ď…ďe waaju immorde ka jurmotoo…óo on fu…ó…óaangu si wonaa …ďe laatike …óuurii…ďe ngu."
  26,6,"GooŇč…óii …ďe njeddii aroyay e ma…ď…ďe kabaruuji ko …ďe laatinoo ko…ďe njalkitano."
  26,7,"Enee, …ďe nji'aani fa'ade e leydi ndin, no foti heewde ko Min pu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone teddu…óo?"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] aaya, …ďur…ďe heew…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko KaŇčko woni teddu…óo Jurmetee…óo On."
  26,10,"JaŇčto tuma nde Joomi maa…óa noddunoo Muusaa, …óum woni ar e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďe."
  26,11,"Yim…ďe Fir'awna, kaa on kulataa"
  26,12,"O maaki: ""Joom am , min mi…óo huli wota …ďe njeddam."
  26,13,"∆Āernde am nden …ďittoo hara …óemngal am ngal wellitaaki, awa Nul to Haaruuna."
  26,14,"No woodani …ďe e dow am bakkaat mi…óo huli fii wota …ďe mbaram."
  26,15,"O Daali: ""Wonaa non, njahee onon …ói…óo, Mi…óen ngon'di e moo…óon ko Min he…óii…ďe""."
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna wi'on: ""Minen dey ko min Nulaa…ďe Jooma winndere nden."""
  26,17,"∆äuum woni accitu …ďi…ó…ďe Isra'iila …ďen wond'ude e amen."
  26,18,"O wi'i: ""Enee, min ne'aano ma ka amin …óoo hari ko a boobo, √Īii…ďu…óaa ka amin …óoo duu…ďi e ngurndam maa…óam?"""
  26,19,"NGollu…óaa gollal maa…óa ngal ngolluno…óaa ngal, an ko e yeddu…ďe …ďen njeya…óaa."
  26,20,"O maaki: ""Mi wa…óii …óum, ontuma min ko mi jiyaa…óo e majju…ďe …ďeen""."
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi kulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal o wa…óin mi jiyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,22,"∆äum ko neema mo mbajitirtaa mi …óum, fii a maccin…óinii …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen."
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: "" Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nde?"""
  26,24,"O maaki: ""Ko Jooma kammuuji …óin e leydi ndi e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaa…ďe."""
  26,25,"O wi'ani …ďeen won…ďe banŇče makko: ""Enee; on le…óataako?"""
  26,26,"O maaki: ""Joomi moo…óon e Jooma baabiraa…ďe adii…ďe …ďen."""
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""Pellet, Nulaa…óo moo…óon on Nulaa…óo fa'ade e moo…óon ko o kaangaa…óo."""
  26,28,"O maaki: ""Ko Jooma funna'ange e hirna'ange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike kakkiloo…ďe."""
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""Mi woo…óndii si jogitike dewetee…óo tan am, mi wa…óete jiyaa…óo dummbaa…ďe …ďeen""."
  26,30,"O maaki: ""enee, hay si mi addanii ma hu'unde …ďanngunde?"""
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""Awa addu …óum, si tawii ko e gooŇč…óu …ďe …ďe njiyaa…óaa."""
  26,32,"O wernii tuggordu makko ndu, jaka ko ndu mboo…ódi (ngoolwa) …ďannguba."
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngo, jaka yoo ko ngo ranwungo wonan'de ndaaroo…ďe …ďe."
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngu fee makko: ""Pellet, oo…óoo ko bileejo keew…óo ganndal""."
  26,35,"Homo fa'andii jaltinirgol on ka leydi moo…óon mbilewu makko ngu. Ko hul…óun njamir…óon?"
  26,36,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Nee…ďnu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ca'e …óen moo…ďoo…ďe (wilee…ďe)""."
  26,37,"∆Āe ngddane kala bileejo ganndu…óo."
  26,38,"Wilee…ďe …ďen moo…ďaa fii fodoore √Īalaande anndaande."
  26,39,"Yim…ďe …ďen mbii'anaa: ""Taw si onon ko on moo…ďike(ndenndi)"""
  26,40,"Mbelejo'o lajo'o minen min njokkay wilee…ďe …ďen, si …ďe laatike ko kam…ďe ngoni fool…ďe …ďen."
  26,41,"Tuma nde wilee…ďe …ďen ngrnoo; …ďe mbi'ani Fir'awna: ""Enee, no woodani min njo…ďdi si tawii ko min ngoni fool…ďe …ďe?"""
  26,42,"O wi'i : ""Eyyo, on tuma on njeyaama e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďen""."
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ďe: ""mbeddee, ko mbernoton kon""."
  26,44,"∆Āe li…ďi …ďoggi ma…ď…ďe e cawoy ma…ď…ďe kon, …ďe mbi'i: ""Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko minen ngoni fooloo…ďe …ďe""."
  26,45,"Muusaa wernii tuggordu makko ndu, tawi kayru hundu mo…óa ko …ďe fekindii ko."
  26,46,"Wilee…ďe …ďe nduuyi …ďe cujji."
  26,47,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Min ngoŇč…óinii Jey…óo Winndere nde,"
  26,48,"Joomum Muusaa e Haaruuna""."
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""Enee, on ngooŇč…óinat mo, ko adii mi duŇčanaade on? Pellet, ko kaŇčko woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngu, kono a nganndon, mami ta∆ī juu…óe moo…óon e koy…óe moo…óon [ta∆īa] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fof moo…óon""."
  26,50,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Tanaa alaa, minen ko fa'ade ka Joomi amin min nduttotoo""."
  26,51,"Minen mi…óen tam∆īinii nde Joomi amin yawtani min ngoopi amin …óin,tawde min laatike adii…ďe gooŇč…óinnde …ďen."
  26,52,"Min mbahayini fa'ade e Muusaa: ""∆äuum woni ro∆īidu e Jiyaa…ďe Am …ďeen. Pellet, onon ko on jokkitetee…ďe""."
  26,53,"Fir'awna nuli to ca'e moo…ďoo…ďe."
  26,54,"[O wi'i:] Pellet, …ďee ko …ďe mojobum pamarum."
  26,55,"Pellet, kam…ďe he…ďe tikkinnde min."
  26,56,"Enen non en fof ko en reentii…ďe."
  26,57,"Min njaltini …ďe immorde e gese e caatli."
  26,58,"E ngaluuji e √Īii…ďirde teddunde."
  26,59,"Ko wano nii, Min ndonini …óum …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen."
  26,60,"∆Āe njokki…ďe de pu…óal."
  26,61,"Tuma nde jamaaji …óin …óin yi'ndirnoo, yim…ďe Muusaa …ďe mbi'i: ""Enen en hewtoyte""."
  26,62,"O maaki: ""∆äuum wa…óataa, pellet, Joomi am no won'di e am o feewnat kam""."
  26,63,"Min mbahayini e Muusaa, …óum woni piyir tuggordu maa…óa ndu maayo ngon, ngo seekii ceekol kala seekol na foti e tulde mawnde."
  26,64,"Min …ďanni ton heddii…ďe …ďe."
  26,65,"Min nda…óni di Muusaa e won'…óu…ďe e makko …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe."
  26,66,"Refti Min njooli heddii …ďe …ďe."
  26,67,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,68,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko KaŇčko woni Teddu…óo jurmetee…óo."
  26,69,"Janngan …ďe kumpital fii Ibraahiima."
  26,70,"Tuma nde o wi'annoo baaba makko e yim…ďe makko …ďe; ko hol…óum ndewoton?"
  26,71,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Mi…óen rewde sanamuuji, min √Īallat ufnanaade …ói""."
  26,72,"O maaki: ""mati i hi…ói nanana on, nde noddoton""."
  26,73,"Maa hi…ói nafa on ma …ói lorra on?"
  26,74,"∆Āe mb'i: ""Ko woni, men tawii baabiraa…ďe amen …ďe konii …ďe ngolliratnoo""."
  26,75,"O maaki: ""Enee, on nji'ii kon ko ngon…óon e rewde?"""
  26,76,"Onon e baabiraa…ďe mon adinoo…ďe …ďe."
  26,77,"Pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe a√Ī…ďe am, si wonaa Jooma winndire nden."
  26,78,"On Tal…óo kam, ko KaŇčko feewnata kam."
  26,79,"On ko KaŇčko √Īamminta kam O yarnan-mi."
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii, ko KaŇčko sellinta kam."
  26,81,"E oon baray…óo kam refti o wurnitan mi."
  26,82,"Oon mo mi tam∆īinii kadi nde O yaafatoomi goopi am …óin √Ďande [njo…ďdi] Diina ka."
  26,83,"Joomam, okkam Ganndal wattidaa mi e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďe."
  26,84,"Mba…óanaa kam jaŇčto mo∆ī∆īo ka sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  26,85,"Mba…óaa mi jiyaa…óo e ronoo…ďe Aljanna Neemaaji …óin."
  26,86,"Njaaf…óaa baaba am, pellet, kaŇčko o laatinoke jiyaa…óo e majju…ďe …ďeen."
  26,87,"Wota A hersinoyam √Ďande …ďe Immital."
  26,88,"√Ďande nde jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe nafataa."
  26,89,"Si wonaa on ardu…óo ka Alla e …ďernde hisnde."
  26,90,"Aljanna oon …ďatinanee huloo…ďe Alla …ďeen."
  26,91,"Jahiim ngeen fe√Ī√Īinanee bew…ďe …ďern."
  26,92,"∆Āe wi'nee: ""Honto woni ko laatino…óon kon ho…óon ndewa""."
  26,93,"Ga Alla? Taw si …ói walla on ma …ói wallat hoore majji?"
  26,94,"∆Āe kippee e ndeer magge kam…ďe e bew…ďe …ďen."
  26,95,"E konnuuji ibliisa …óiin …ói fof majji."
  26,96,"∆Āe mbi'i tawi kam…ďe he…ďe wennjondira ndeer ton:"
  26,97,"""Min woondirii Alla, min woniino e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde."
  26,98,"Tuma nde min njeddunoo on e Jooma winndere nde"""
  26,99,"Majjinaani min si ngonaa bon…ďe …ďen."
  26,100,"Alanaa min tefoo…ďe."
  26,101,"Wonaa kadi gi…óo √Īallam…ďereejo(tigi tigi)."
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo min ndutteede, min laatoo jiyaa…ďe e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] aaya, …ďur…ďe heew…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kako woni Teddu…óo jurmetee…óo."
  26,105,"Yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen njeddii Nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on mbiannoo …ďe: ""Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?"""
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi nulaa…óo e moo…óon koolaa…óo."
  26,108,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,110,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,111,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Enee, hara men ngooŇč…óinte, ja'as…ďe …ďen no njokkumaa?"""
  26,112,"O maaki: ""Ko hol…óum woni ganndal am e ko …ďe ngonoo e gollude?""."
  26,113,"Hasboore ma…ď…ďe nde fawaaki si wonaa e Joomi am, sinndo ho…óon so'aynoo."
  26,114,"Min mi ngonaani ra…óotoo…óo gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  26,115,"Min mi ngonaani si wonaa jerrtinoowo …ďanngu…óo."
  26,116,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Min woondii si a accaani aan Nuuhu, ma a laato sanne jiyaa…óo e rajmetee…ďe …ďen""."
  26,117,"O maaki: ""Joom am, pellet, yim…ďe am …ďen …ďe fenni kam""."
  26,118,"√Ďaawu hakkunde am e ma…ď…ďe √Īaawoore, ndanndaa mi e …ďeen wonndu…ďe e am joyaa…ďe e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  26,119,"Min danndi mo e …ďeen won'…óu…ďe e makko ka ndeer laana ∆īoltiika(loowaaka)."
  26,120,"Refti Min yooli …ďaawo [ma…ď…ďe] heddii…ďe …ďen."
  26,121,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,122,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko KaŇčko woni Teddu…óo jurmetee…óo."
  26,123,"AadiŇčkoo…ďe …ďen njeddiino Nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,124,"Tuma nde Huudu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: ""Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?"""
  26,125,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon koolaa…óo."
  26,126,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,127,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óuum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,128,"Enee, on mahat Ma'ande e kala tulde ho…óon pija?"
  26,129,"Njogito…óon ku…ďeeje a wi'ayma onon ko on luttintee…ďe [ka aduna]."
  26,130,"Si on njaggitii, njanggiton ko ndunndarankoo…ďe."
  26,131,"Lulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,132,"Kulee oon …ďeydir…óo on ko nganndu…óon."
  26,133,"O …ďeydiri on neemoraa…ói e …ďi…ď…ďe wor…ďe."
  26,134,"E gese e can…ói.(gite)."
  26,135,"[O maaki] min dey, mi…óo hulani on Lepte √Ďalaande mawnde."
  26,136,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""No fotana min ter, si a waajike ma si a laataaki jiyaa…óo e waajotoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  26,137,"Pellet, …óuum wonaani si wonaa jikku adinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  26,138,"Minen Min ngonaani leptoytee…ďe."
  26,139,"∆Āe njeddi mo, Min kalki …ďe. Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko KaŇčko woni Teddu…óo jurmetee…óo."
  26,141,"SamuudiŇčkoo…ďe …ďeen njeddiino Nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: ""Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?"""
  26,143,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon koolaa…óo."
  26,144,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,145,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óuum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndi fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,146,"Enee, hara on ngaccete e koo ko woni …óoo ko on hoolii…ďe?!"
  26,147,"E ndeer gese e can…ói.(gote.)"
  26,148,"E remuruuji e tamarooje hara dukke majje ko …ďenndu…óe."
  26,149,"Ho…óon lesa pelle …óeen [mba…óon] cuu…ói ko on haawitii…ďe."
  26,150,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,151,"Wota on …óofto jamaruyee fantinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  26,152,"∆Āeen bonnoo…ďe ka leydi hara …ďe mo∆ī∆īintaa."
  26,153,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Pellet, an ko a jiyaa…óo wilaa…ďe …ďeen""."
  26,154,"An a wonaani si wonaa …ďannduŇčke yeru amen, awa addu aaya, si tawii a laatike jiyaa…óo e gooŇč…óuu…ďe …ďen."
  26,155,"O maaki: ""baa…óoo ko naaqawa, no woodani mba yarannde, no woodani on onon kadi yarannde √Īalaande anndaande""."
  26,156,"Wota on memir mba ko boni, sakko nannga on Lepte √Ďande Mawnde."
  26,157,"∆Āe mborii mba, …ďe ngonti nimsu…ďe."
  26,158,"Lepte …óen nanngi …ďe. Pellet, ngonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,159,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kako woni Teddu…óo Jurmetee…óo."
  26,160,"Yim…ďe Luutu …ďeen njeddi Nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,161,"Tuma nde Luutu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: ""Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?"""
  26,162,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon koolaa…óo."
  26,163,"Kulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,164,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,165,"Enee, on ngarat e wor…ďe …ďe immorde e winndere nde?!"
  26,166,"∆äalon ko Joomi moo…óon tagani on kon immorde e sonnaa…ďe moo…óon? Ko woni, onon ko on yim…ďe yawtu…ďe Keerol."
  26,167,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Min ngoo…óndiri si a accaani aan Luutu, ma a laato sanne jiyaa…óo e yaltitee…ďe …ďen""."
  26,168,"O maaki: ""Min dey, mi…óo jiyaa e a√Ī…ďe …ďen golle moo…óon …óen""."
  26,169,"Jooma, danndam min e …ďeynguure am ndeen kon ko …ďe ngollata."
  26,170,"Min danndi mo e …ďeynguure makko nden, …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe."
  26,171,"Si wonaa jiidiraare(nayeejo debbo) nden ka halkaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,172,"Refti Min o∆ī∆īi heddii …ďe …ďen."
  26,173,"Min to…ďini e dow ma…ď…ďe to…ďo, bonii to…ďo jeertinaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,174,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] aaya, …ďur…ďe heewu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki mgooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,175,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kako woni Teddu…óo Jurmetee…óo."
  26,176,"Yim…ďe fitaare(sutu) nden njeddiino Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  26,177,"Tuma nde Su'aybu wi'annoo …ďe: ""Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?"""
  26,178,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon koolaa…óo."
  26,179,"Lulee Alla …óofto…óon mi."
  26,180,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óuum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,181,"Kumnee …ďetu ngu, wata on laato jiyaa…ďe e ustoo…ďe …ďeen."
  26,182,"Manndikiree(pe'esir…óe) manndikir…óe peew…óe …óeen."
  26,183,"Wata on ustan yim…ďe …ďen piiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, wota on lancito ka leydi hara ko on bonnoo…ďe."
  26,184,"Kulee oon Tak…óo on, o tagoore adinoongu ngun."
  26,185,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Pellet, an ko a jiyaa…óo wilaa…ďe …ďen."
  26,186,"Aan a wonaani si wonaa …ďannduŇčke yeru amen, tawde mi…óen cikkumaa ko a jiyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďeen."
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jiyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  26,188,"O maaki: ""Ko Joomi am woni ganndu…óo ko ngolloton kon""."
  26,189,"∆Āe njeddi mo, nanngi …ďe Lepte √Īalaande …óowdiinde nden. Pellet, …óen laatino Lepte √Īalaande mawnde."
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] aaya, …ďur…ďe heew…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko KaŇčko woni Teddu…óo Jurmetee…óo."
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Joom winndere nde."
  26,193,"Jippinii nde ruuhu koolaa…óo oon."
  26,194,"E …ďernde maa…óa fii yo a laato jiyaa…óo e jeertinoo…ďe …ďen."
  26,195,"E …óemngal Aarabi …ďanngungal."
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hende ka …óeri aran…ďe …ďeen."
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki …ďe Ma'ande, nde tawata anndiino nde …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila anndu…ďe …ďen?"
  26,198,"Sinndo Min njippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyaŇčkoo…ďe …ďen."
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe laatotaako goo…óin…ďe nde."
  26,200,"Ko wano nii Min naatniri …óum e …ďer…óe bon…ďe …ďen."
  26,201,"∆Āe ngooŇč…óintaa nde, haa …ďe nji'a Lepte mu'usu…óe …óen."
  26,202,"∆äe ngara e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee, hara …ďe so'aa."
  26,203,"Sakko …ďe mbi'a: ""Taw si ko min nee…ďnantee…ďe?"""
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte amen …óen …ďe ke√Īorta?"
  26,205,"A tinii si Min ndakmitii …ďe duu…ďi."
  26,206,"Refti ari e ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďe podee."
  26,207,"Nafaali …ďe ko …ďe laatinoo kon he…ďe ndakmitoo."
  26,208,"Min kalkatanii saare woo, si wonaa hara no woodani nde jeertinoo…ďe."
  26,209,"[∆äuum] ko waaju, Min laataaki too√Īoo…ďe."
  26,210,"Wonaa seytanuuji …óin njippini nde."
  26,211,"[∆äuum] haananaa…ói, …ói kattantaa …óum kadi."
  26,212,"Pellet, kannji ko …ói follatee…ói ga ke…óagol ngol."
  26,213,"Wota a noddu dewetee…óo goo wond'ude e Alla, sakko laato…óaa jiyaa…óo e Leptetee…ďe …ďen."
  26,214,"Jeertin gorol maa…óa …ďur…ďe …ďadaade …ďen."
  26,215,"Les…óinan balbe maa…óen, wona nde …ďen jokku…ďe ma immorde e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  26,216,"Si …ďe njeddii ma, haray maaku: ""Min dey, ko mi danndii…óo ko ngolloton""."
  26,217,"Hoolor On Teddu…óo Jurmetee…óo."
  26,218,"On jioowo ma saha de daroto…óaa."
  26,219,"E baylitogol maa…óa e hakkunde sujjoo…ďe …ďeen."
  26,220,"Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo ganndu…óo On."
  26,221,"Taw si mi humpitay on ko e hommbo Seytanuuji …óin njippotoo?"
  26,222,"Hi…ói njippoo e dow kala fekindotoo…óo bakkodin…óo."
  26,223,"Hi…ói mbernoo nan…óe …óen, ko …ďur…ďe heewude e majji ko penooji."
  26,224,"Yimoo…ďe …ďeen ko jokkata …ďe, ko bew…ďe …ďeen."
  26,225,"Enee, a tinaani won'dema kam…ďe he…ďe yinoo e kala aynde?"
  26,226,"E tawde kam…ďe he…ďe wowla ko …ďe ngollataa."
  26,227,"Si wonaa …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe …ďe njaŇčtii Alla ko …óuu…ói …ďe yo…ďtii …ďaawo …ďe too√Īaama. Aray ka …ďeen too√Īu…ďe annday ko honde e waylitorde …ďe mbaylitotoo."
